    "causal_summary": "Packets 071/072 + the inline telemetry-schema fix surfaced 4 bounded toolchain issues. 3 are mechanical fixes (run-matrix.sh token-extraction regexes for codex+opencode; opencode 120s→180s timeout; post-save reviewer EISDIR guard). The 4th (test-alignment-validator.js ESM bug) turned out to need a deeper refactor — the validator source uses `import.meta.url` which can't be transpiled to CommonJS. Bundling fixed#2/3/4 into one cleanup keeps the diff coherent; deferring #1 to a focused follow-up packet preserves scope.",
